name: USDTRAVEL
description: USD Travel (USDT) is more than a cryptocurrency; it is a solution designed for the global citizen. By directly addressing the inefficiencies and high costs of traditional currency exchange, USDT empowers travelers with a financial tool that is powerful, secure, and easy to use. Our mission is to redefine how the world thinks about money while traveling, creating a future where cross-border transactions are as seamless as exploring a new destination.
